What... What happened?

91
00:10:56,730 --> 00:10:59,629
- Are you all right?
- Yes, I'm fine. I'm not hurt much.

92
00:11:01,070 --> 00:11:03,529
- Did you hurt your arm?
- Yes, I think I sprained it.

93
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,470
- But I'm fine.
- Let me take a look.

94
00:11:05,539 --> 00:11:06,669
I'm really okay.

95
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,340
- Let me see.
- Mr. Choi.

96
00:11:11,909 --> 00:11:13,879
What do you think you're doing?

97
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:16,710
What will you do
if these people here got infected too?

98
00:11:17,149 --> 00:11:20,519
Sir, they are not infected.

99
00:11:21,289 --> 00:11:23,490
They're just people who needed our help.

100
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:26,960
Then what about them?

101
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:32,799
If you put us in danger
just to save these two,

102
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:34,470
will you take full responsibility?

103
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:38,240
Mr. Seo, what are you waiting for?

104
00:11:38,299 --> 00:11:40,340
Kick them out of here!

105
00:11:43,169 --> 00:11:44,240
Enough.

106
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:47,179
I feel disgusted by you.

107
00:11:47,809 --> 00:11:50,549
- What?
- Don't pretend you care about others.

108
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:52,320
I know you're doing this
only to protect yourself, Father!

109
00:11:52,379 --> 00:11:54,090
