Just look at my eyes.

118
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,350
Do my eyes look like
the ones of an infected?

119
00:12:28,419 --> 00:12:32,659
I guess we'll have to wait and see
whether you're right or not.

120
00:12:34,889 --> 00:12:38,600
Now, let go of my arm.
Are you trying to break it?

121
00:12:48,409 --> 00:12:50,539
(Muji Hospital)

122
00:12:51,179 --> 00:12:53,009
- Is everything okay?
- Yes, everything's fine.

123
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,080
