134
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:21,009
I have to go and bring back Ji Hye.

135
00:13:21,710 --> 00:13:22,940
Calm down.

136
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:25,009
What will you do
with the infected inside the hospital?

137
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:27,240
She's with other people.

138
00:13:27,309 --> 00:13:28,879
I'm sure she's safe there.

139
00:13:29,049 --> 00:13:31,620
The rescue is on the way,
so let's just wait a little longer.

140
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:33,580
Don't lie.

141
00:13:34,950 --> 00:13:38,360
You know
that no one's coming to rescue us.

142
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,029
I'll go with you.

143
00:13:49,299 --> 00:13:50,669
You know the building well, right?

144
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:52,870
Take us to the 5th floor surgical ward.

145
00:13:53,769 --> 00:13:56,740
I haven't worked here for long so...

146
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,379
Wait, wait, wait.

147
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:02,879
What do you mean
you're going to another ward?

148
00:14:03,179 --> 00:14:05,450
There are survivors on another floor.

149
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:06,980
We're going to rescue them.

150
00:14:07,049 --> 00:14:08,389
Is there anyone else who wants to help?

151
00:14:08,450 --> 00:14:09,590
Wait a minute.

152
00:14:10,049 --> 00:14:12,789
So you're saying
you're going to rescue those people?

153
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,490
Is that why you're making such a fuss?

154
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:16,759
A fuss? To save people?

155
00:14:17,059 --> 00:14:19,460
Yes, you are making such a fuss.

156
00:14:19,529 --> 00:14:21,970
What if the infected get in here?

157
00:14:22,029 --> 00:14:24,269
- What will you do if that happens?
- If those people were your family,

158
00:14:24,340 --> 00:14:25,840
would you have said the same?

159
00:14:28,509 --> 00:14:29,809
Hey, look.

160
00:14:32,809 --> 00:14:35,779
Why are you acting like a cop?

161
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:37,279
Who are you?

162
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:41,090
You were fired for accepting a bribe.
Who are you to rescue someone?

163
00:14:43,490 --> 00:14:45,360
(Homicide Squad 1)

164
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,629
How did it go?

165
00:14:49,059 --> 00:14:50,360
What do you think?

166
00:14:51,659 --> 00:14:52,659
I got fired.

167
00:14:53,759 --> 00:14:56,330
I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

168
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:58,370
Why would you be?

169
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:00,570
What? Well...

170
00:15:01,509 --> 00:15:04,610
I don't know who's responsible for this,
but if I catch that son of a gun...

171
00:15:05,509 --> 00:15:07,950
Don't overreact.
I'll be just fine without this job.

172
00:15:12,019 --> 00:15:13,120
Let's go have a drink.

173
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:21,629
What? You know I'm not making things up.

174
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,600
Isn't that right, Officer Park?

175
00:15:29,669 --> 00:15:32,070
So don't make a fuss.

176
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:35,710
Get lost if you're not here to help.

177
00:15:39,340 --> 00:15:40,980
