- Excuse me.
- Yes?

190
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:44,000
Do you think she can make it to
the 4th floor Negative Pressure Room?

191
00:17:45,799 --> 00:17:47,069
What are you planning?

192
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:50,609
Excuse me. You're not planning
to get out of here, are you?

193
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:54,109
The infected disappeared just now.

194
00:17:54,309 --> 00:17:56,210
Now is the time to get moving.

195
00:17:56,349 --> 00:17:58,619
You're going to open the door?

196
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:02,519
Then should we all just die here?

197
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:05,559
Still, it's dangerous
to head out by ourselves!

198
00:18:05,859 --> 00:18:08,859
I think it's better to wait for
a rescue team or the police.

199
00:18:08,930 --> 00:18:10,089
Isn't it?

200
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:13,299
I also think it'll be more dangerous
for us to go out.

201
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,900
Her condition is not looking good.

202
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:18,700
We need to get her to safety quickly.

203
00:18:18,769 --> 00:18:21,769
Darn it! Nowhere's safe now.

204
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:24,410
Wouldn't the Negative Pressure Room
on the 4th floor be safe?

205
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:30,609
You're right. The place is equipped
with an air pressure regulator,

206
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:33,150
so we can block out the smoke.

207
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:36,390
The door is also double-layered, so the
infected won't be able to get in easily.

208
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:38,589
Look. Maybe we can get there by ourselves,

209
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:41,559
but how can we go all the way there
with a pregnant woman?

210
00:18:41,630 --> 00:18:44,430
If the infected suddenly attacks,
what will we do?

211
00:18:45,099 --> 00:18:46,829
I'll try my best to stop them.

212
00:18:50,329 --> 00:18:52,769
I'll lead the way. The rest of you,

213
00:18:52,839 --> 00:18:55,069
focus on protecting her.

214
00:18:56,069 --> 00:18:57,309
What should we do?

215
00:18:59,009 --> 00:19:00,880
Hey,

216
00:19:00,910 --> 00:19:02,849
let's stop overthinking.

217
00:19:02,910 --> 00:19:04,180
Whatever happens,

218
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:07,250
