who works for the government.

219
00:19:07,450 --> 00:19:08,990
Darn it.

220
00:19:09,690 --> 00:19:10,589
All right.

221
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:15,529
Then grab something
you can use as a weapon.

222
00:19:24,869 --> 00:19:26,240
Thank you for your work.

223
00:19:33,940 --> 00:19:35,309
Are you all right?

224
00:19:35,450 --> 00:19:37,079
Thank you for your help earlier.

225
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,250
It must've been difficult
to muster up the courage.

226
00:19:39,319 --> 00:19:40,779
It's nothing.

227
00:19:40,849 --> 00:19:43,390
It's best to save as many as possible.

228
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:48,430
But why did the black smoke
and the infected...

229
00:19:48,589 --> 00:19:50,559
suddenly disappear earlier?

230
00:19:52,930 --> 00:19:56,599
I think they reacted to a bizarre sound
with high frequency.

231
