High-frequency sound?

232
00:20:00,099 --> 00:20:03,569
I didn't hear anything.

233
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,180
Really?

234
00:20:07,410 --> 00:20:08,480
Yes.

235
00:20:15,819 --> 00:20:19,589
The sound that only you can hear,

236
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:21,589
what do you think it is?

237
00:20:21,660 --> 00:20:23,490
I'm not sure,

238
00:20:23,730 --> 00:20:26,230
but judging from
how all the infected stopped attacking,

239
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:29,529
I think they're being controlled
by something.

240
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:39,880
Right, I forgot to introduce myself.

241
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:42,650
I'm Choi Seung Tae.

242
00:20:44,849 --> 00:20:47,420
I'm Detective Lee Hwa Seon from Seoul.

243
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:04,839
