244
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:10,509
What happened here?

245
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:12,940
What...

246
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:15,579
What...

247
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:20,180
What on earth happened here?

248
00:21:20,619 --> 00:21:22,220
This is bad!

249
