didn't I tell you to watch over this?

252
00:21:39,299 --> 00:21:41,269
- I did!
- Then,

253
00:21:41,339 --> 00:21:43,539
why is the door broken,

254
00:21:43,609 --> 00:21:45,640
and why is there no cow at all?

255
00:21:46,609 --> 00:21:49,950
You punk, what were you doing...

256
00:21:50,009 --> 00:21:51,680
